issues.title: Enabling Multiuser plugin in 0.6.4 causes Ui to crash
issues.body:
Default config, just renamed disabled-Multiuser to Multiuser in plugins.

Server error
Err: AttributeError: 'NoneType' object has no attribute 'settings' in UiServer.py line 104 > UiRequest.py line 144 > UiConfigPlugin.py line 21 > MultiuserPlugin.py line 56 > ContentFilterPlugin.py line 184 > UiRequest.py line 344 > UiRequest.py line 421
Please report it if you think this an error.
